/*Notice*/
In test cases consisting of "/" and spaces (or just some "/"), `ERROR#540:"Output n°[[Output Number]] is empty".` occurs, so I did not add them because I could not implement the edge cases correctly.
Please let me know if there are any solutions.

/*Addendum*/
I've added the following constraints: "If all output consists of blanks and newlines, please output 'Illegal output'." and "It is guaranteed that not all lines are empty."
